-----------------------------------------------------------------------
RP2040 / Raspberry Pi Pico W port notice

Copyright (c) 2025 Marcin Kielesiński

This distribution contains modifications and platform glue code to run the
WireGuard-ESP32-Arduino library on RP2040-based boards (e.g., Raspberry Pi Pico W)
using the Arduino-Pico core and the CYW43/lwIP network stack.

The ported modifications are provided under the same BSD 3-Clause License as the
original work above.
